WEBVTT

00:00:00.438 --> 00:00:10.505
Good morning, family. I’m going to talk to you about the time when Jesus woke me up in the middle of the night and ministered to me.

00:00:10.506 --> 00:00:20.806
This was around October 2014, and this experience forever changed my life.

00:00:20.807 --> 00:00:36.012
I feel in my heart that when I first started on YouTube, I tried to tell you all what he said, and I thought I would do it again because it gets buried by the algorithm.

00:00:36.013 --> 00:00:50.028
Nobody sees it, especially all the new faces here. I want to tell you because this was an experience I had with him that changed my life forever.

00:00:50.029 --> 00:00:56.335
I was sleeping when, all of a sudden, I felt a tap on my right shoulder.

00:00:56.336 --> 00:01:12.478
I was just laying in bed on my side and I heard an audible voice say, 'Wake up.'I looked over, and Jesus was standing in my room.

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:16.429
Most people will ask, 'Was this a vision?'No, this was not a vision.

00:01:16.430 --> 00:01:27.035
This was real; he manifested in my house. This was one of the only times it was not an open vision.

00:01:27.036 --> 00:01:35.395
This was a face-to-face experience with him touching my shoulder and waking me up.

00:01:35.396 --> 00:01:46.683
It startled me so much because when you're waking up and rubbing your eyes, you don't recognize things immediately. I looked over and saw Jesus standing there.

00:01:46.684 --> 00:01:55.416
I felt his glory and presence and thought, 'Am I dying?'My initial reaction was that I was going home and he was coming to get me.

00:01:55.417 --> 00:02:09.859
But he said, 'I've come to answer your prayers.'I asked, 'Lord, what's happening?'All of a sudden, I looked at my floor, and it was alive.

00:02:09.860 --> 00:02:19.136
The glory of the Lord was so strong in my house that the floor was breathing. A portal opened in my floor.

00:02:19.137 --> 00:02:33.169
I flipped my feet over the side of my bed and sat there looking at that portal below my feet.

00:02:33.170 --> 00:02:45.839
Jesus was standing right there at my right hand. I was looking at this portal, and it was alive; I could feel the air breathing.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:03:02.308
It was blowing my hair. I could feel the breeze from the portal.

00:03:02.309 --> 00:03:14.316
It was moving like a whirlpool, with light moving down and up like a waterfall.

00:03:14.317 --> 00:03:22.688
My wife was sleeping next to me and never knew any of this happened; she was out cold.

00:03:22.689 --> 00:03:48.784
I said, 'Lord, what do you want me to do?'He said, 'I want you to jump inside that portal.'I said, 'You want me to jump?'He said, 'Brandon, trust me.'I looked at him because this was all happening so fast and it was shocking.

00:03:48.785 --> 00:04:00.531
Jesus was standing there in a beautiful white robe, and his hair was flowing because the air from the portal was moving it.

00:04:00.532 --> 00:04:09.409
I said, 'Okay, Lord.'All of a sudden, I pushed myself off the edge of the bed and went straight down into that tunnel.

00:04:09.410 --> 00:04:18.487
It was like Mario Brothers on the Nintendo when you go into the tunnel and they transported you to another part.

00:04:18.488 --> 00:04:28.635
That's what it felt like. When I jumped inside of that hole, I was taken to the past.

00:04:28.636 --> 00:04:35.175
I was standing at a hospital where my wife and I had our daughter, Megan.

00:04:35.176 --> 00:04:43.801
He said, 'Brandon, I'm giving you a chance. You've asked me and asked me to go back in time.

00:04:43.802 --> 00:05:07.990
You always ask, "Lord, if I could just go back in time to when she got her shot and stop that, I could keep her from getting this severe autism."'I’ve always said that I would clean the bathrooms of the church or vacuum the halls if I could just go back in time and warn myself.

00:05:07.991 --> 00:05:23.714
If I could just give myself the opportunity to tell myself not to do that, because it wrecked my life the way it has.

00:05:23.715 --> 00:05:39.763
I wished I could have a redo. He said, 'I'm going to give you the time to go and change the future.

00:05:39.764 --> 00:05:54.255
I want you to go and tell yourself.'I ran up the stairs to the fourth floor of the doctor's office.

00:05:54.256 --> 00:06:03.313
I busted through the doors and saw my younger self sitting there with my daughter and my wife.

00:06:03.314 --> 00:06:18.468
They were getting ready to administer the shot. I said 'Stop!'just like that. I froze, and the younger me froze.

00:06:18.469 --> 00:06:46.965
I told the nurse to stop and told my younger self, 'Don't do it.'All of a sudden, Jesus came and said, 'I want to show you the power of a choice.'He threw his hand open and put a screen up in front of my face.

00:06:46.966 --> 00:07:05.047
Everything froze in time, and he showed me a future where Megan didn't get that shot. He painted it all out in front of me for each year.

00:07:05.048 --> 00:07:23.251
He said, 'Brandon, I want to show you what happened by this choice.'I told him, 'Lord, you've called me to be a healing evangelist, but I can't pray for people because I'll look like a hypocrite while my own daughter is still overcome.

00:07:23.252 --> 00:07:40.143
I've laid hands on her probably a thousand times and never felt the anointing go into her.'I’ve always kept this private.

00:07:40.144 --> 00:07:53.505
I wouldn't even let anyone say the word 'autistic.'I would want to fight you if you did because faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:07:53.506 --> 00:08:05.255
I didn't even let the doctors diagnose her at first because I was so upset; I didn't want them speaking those words because life and death are in the power of the tongue.

00:08:05.256 --> 00:08:25.283
I got really flaky about it because I was scared of the diagnosis and didn't want anyone speaking anything over my child.

00:08:25.284 --> 00:08:32.265
I'm telling you all, it was bondage. And she would rock in the corner and scream at night all night long after it happened.

00:08:32.266 --> 00:08:47.838
I'm telling you, it was literal hell on earth for years before I would allow them to diagnose her and for her to get help through therapies and stuff, because I was believing God by faith because I'm the big healing evangelist and because of all these prophecies that were given over my life.

00:08:47.839 --> 00:09:06.181
So here I am. The Lord threw all this out in front of me and he said, "Brandon, I want to show you what happens with Megan."Now, Megan is developing normally, but you're not changing.

00:09:06.182 --> 00:09:20.984
The pressure from her circumstance changes you. It puts you through the refiner's fire. And he told me, "Brandon, I did not do this.

00:09:20.985 --> 00:09:30.902
I did not cause her to be autistic, but whatever the devil meant for bad, I will turn it for good in your favor.

00:09:30.903 --> 00:09:37.238
And no matter how bad the circumstance is, I will always turn it for good in your favor.

00:09:37.239 --> 00:09:45.838
Whatever the devil meant for bad for you."But he said, "I'm not the one that caused the autism.

00:09:45.839 --> 00:09:51.938
It's a fallen world. Things happen. You know what I'm saying?"That's the way he painted the picture to me.

00:09:51.939 --> 00:09:58.258
I want to say exactly what he said, but it's been so long that I'm forgetting some of the words, so you have to just bear with me here.

00:09:58.259 --> 00:10:10.127
I'm painting the picture of how Jesus told me. So he painted the picture in front of me and I went from year to year. He said, "Brandon, do you see right here?

00:10:10.128 --> 00:10:19.039
You have a lot of anger issues that you're still overcoming."And he said, "You were very verbally abusive to your wife,"which I was.

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:25.735
I belittled her a lot when I first got married. I was young and stupid and I didn't handle myself like I should.

00:10:25.736 --> 00:10:37.518
And he said, because of this right here, it develops a wall between you and your wife over the course of time.

00:10:37.519 --> 00:11:00.322
Megan's developing normally, but he said your wife leaves you right here—and he pointed out the year, which is nobody's business—but he told me, "She is going to leave you right here and she takes your daughter and they move to Texas."And he said, "And you see her every two weeks on the weekends.

00:11:00.323 --> 00:11:05.807
You don't have full custody because she moves and lives with her mom.

00:11:05.808 --> 00:11:16.598
Whenever this takes place, you see her on the weekends."And he said, Diana gets remarried to another man.

00:11:16.599 --> 00:11:29.093
And he showed me the man and said, "This is when your wife gets remarried."And he said, "Then you become very bitter and angry because of the choices that you've made.

00:11:29.094 --> 00:11:39.619
You're off track with your call and what I've called you to do because this is what's changing you.

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:45.359
All this pressure from having a child with special needs is molding your character.

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:50.456
It's breaking you down. It's making you pliable in my hands.

00:11:50.457 --> 00:12:01.159
Yes, the pressure—I did not do it, but I will use it."Does that make sense?

00:12:01.160 --> 00:12:16.048
So I saw the pressure of my daughter every single year without having the pressure from this because she didn't have the autism anymore; she became normal and she became an adult.

00:12:16.049 --> 00:12:32.795
And he said, "Brandon, your son was never born. Your son that your wife has right now was never born, and your daughter that will be born in the future will not be born.

00:12:32.796 --> 00:12:40.459
And there is a call on her life for the thousand years for things that I'm going to do with a thousand years.

00:12:40.460 --> 00:13:05.242
There are things that are set in motion that will not be put in motion because of choices."He said, "You say that you've messed up your life and you can't be used now because of Megan."But he said, "Brandon, all things work together for good for those that love the Lord and are heirs and are called according to his purpose.

00:13:05.243 --> 00:13:34.295
You're not big enough to mess up your life. You're not big enough to derail your life."He said, "If you are in right standing with me and you keep yourself in right standing and seek me daily, building your relationship with me, I will take what the devil meant for bad and turn it for good in your favor.

00:13:34.296 --> 00:13:39.362
There's not enough power in hell to derail the call on your life, son.

00:13:39.363 --> 00:13:50.702
Even with how bad you feel you've messed up with this, I'll turn it around for good in your favor if you keep seeking me."So I want to tell you this.

00:13:50.703 --> 00:14:04.289
Whenever he told me this, I saw each year play out before my face, up until that point. My son wasn't born; my youngest daughter wasn't born.

00:14:04.290 --> 00:14:14.622
All these bad decisions that I had made and the pressure I had from having a child with special needs had molded me to what I am today.

00:14:14.623 --> 00:14:24.578
And God took what the devil meant for bad and he turned it around for good in my favor because it molded me and created a better person out of me.

00:14:24.579 --> 00:14:38.782
If you've never been a caretaker of somebody with special needs whenever they're messing themselves or having their cycle or going through the hell that I went through in the beginning, the tears that I cried...

00:14:38.783 --> 00:14:47.832
she only slept two hours a night. It was awful. And that lasted for years. I would go to work and I would be so tired.

00:14:47.833 --> 00:15:02.766
I'd fall asleep laying against the wall and I'd catch myself because I was so tired cleaning toilets, and I was barely making any money at all, living on food stamps for years.

00:15:02.767 --> 00:15:12.852
I'm doing this and my wife is at home crying and I can't wait to get home. I can't deal with this anymore because Megan was so bad.

00:15:12.853 --> 00:15:37.772
And she'd say, "Can you come and relieve me and just get the car?"because we only had one car, "and drive her around just so she'll fall asleep while you're driving around."Because we couldn't even get her to fall asleep in the house because even clothes—she didn't wear clothes for years because the touch of the clothing on her skin weirded her out and she'd have to take her clothes off.

00:15:37.773 --> 00:15:51.030
Everybody was thinking, "Well, this kid's just wearing a diaper."We got her to where she'd wear a diaper in public because she didn't even want to have a diaper on, and so she'd try to be nude because she didn't want the texture of the diaper on.

00:15:51.031 --> 00:15:56.358
So we had to get her to the point where she would just wear a diaper, and we were ecstatic about that.

00:15:56.359 --> 00:16:04.398
Then we were ecstatic just to get a t-shirt on her, or one of those big princess dresses.

00:16:04.399 --> 00:16:08.883
We tried to put one of those nightgowns on her, so she would walk around with a nightgown on.

00:16:08.884 --> 00:16:17.274
It took us another year or so before we got her there. And it was like all this time was pressure, pressure, pressure.

00:16:17.275 --> 00:16:22.700
And it molds you. And what happens with the diamond whenever that coal is under pressure?

00:16:22.701 --> 00:16:33.295
It transforms into something so beautiful. But without the pressure, it would never transform into what it was supposed to be.

00:16:33.296 --> 00:16:40.324
Just like it is with a caterpillar. You have a beautiful caterpillar in a cocoon.

00:16:40.325 --> 00:16:58.043
And if you remove that cocoon before it's time and they don't have the strength—the monarch butterfly has the strength to push against that cocoon—it will never develop the strength to fly.

00:16:58.044 --> 00:17:10.656
The pressure of the cocoon makes that caterpillar that turns into a butterfly into who it is.

00:17:10.657 --> 00:17:28.959
And without that pressure on its life, it will never be what it's supposed to be because we think, "Well, we'll just remove that off of there."But if you remove that pressure of him trying to fight to get out of that, that caterpillar wouldn't be a beautiful monarch butterfly.

00:17:28.960 --> 00:17:43.023
So, a lot of times I see what people go through. They think that the storms of life are destroying them, but yet they're making them into who they are. The pressure of life develops you into something great.

00:17:43.024 --> 00:17:58.194
We think, 'God, can you remove this or that?'But He tells you today, 'All things are possible to him that believes.'And not only that, 'Son, I'm going to turn it around for good.

00:17:58.195 --> 00:18:05.689
What the devil meant for bad, I'm going to turn for good in your favor.'That's what He's trying to tell you all.

00:18:05.690 --> 00:18:13.489
Don't always embrace it; fight and resist it. Just like that caterpillar is up there fighting and that butterfly is going, 'I want out of this!

00:18:13.490 --> 00:18:21.038
I want out of this!'Fight spiritually against it. Don't embrace it and coddle it.

00:18:21.039 --> 00:18:28.272
Resist it. Submit yourself therefore unto God. Resist the devil and he will flee.

00:18:28.273 --> 00:18:36.293
But when trials and things happen, we fight against them and we won't let them stay.

00:18:36.294 --> 00:18:44.785
But the process of the fight is what changes us. A lot of times it's the word; it's staying the course.

00:18:44.786 --> 00:18:53.163
And in this situation, like I said, God did not do this. The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:18:53.164 --> 00:18:57.436
But the Bible says that He has come that we might have life, and life more abundantly.

00:18:57.437 --> 00:19:05.155
But in this situation, it's what I needed obviously to develop who I was a little bit more.

00:19:05.156 --> 00:19:14.308
And whenever it was all over, He preached me a sermon. He encouraged me and told me there was a call on my life. He told me that He was going to use me for ministry.

00:19:14.309 --> 00:19:33.519
He told me that this pressure that I was going through at the time would subside, that the storms of life would not always be there with the intensity of what it was then, but that we would always go from glory to glory to glory and we mature and we are able to handle that pressure a little better.

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:37.918
There's more pressure now than I've ever had before. But it's different.

00:19:37.919 --> 00:19:44.613
It's different because we're going from glory to glory, and that potter is putting His hand on that clay and He's molding us.

00:19:44.614 --> 00:19:50.417
We have this treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of us.

00:19:50.418 --> 00:19:56.620
And if you think, 'Well, I've derailed my life. I was a bad person. I murdered, I raped, I robbed.

00:19:56.621 --> 00:20:03.940
I did whatever, and God can't use me now,'or 'I was the victim of that,'—that's what I'm trying to say.

00:20:03.941 --> 00:20:08.607
You say, 'I was the victim of a rape. I was a victim of an abusive husband.

00:20:08.608 --> 00:20:16.074
I was a victim of a sexually abusive father, or all these things, and I'm disqualified. God can't use me.

00:20:16.075 --> 00:20:22.168
I'm broken.'What the devil meant for bad to destroy you, God will turn it around in your favor.

00:20:22.169 --> 00:20:31.999
What was meant to try to derail and destroy you, He will take and turn into beauty from ashes.

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:44.265
And I'm telling you, don't give up on what you are believing for because those circumstances and that pain are what's going to help you to help somebody else that's walked through the pain and is walking through it right now.

00:20:44.266 --> 00:20:48.765
You'll be able to minister to somebody and have compassion on them when somebody else won't.

00:20:48.766 --> 00:20:54.008
Like somebody who's been diagnosed with something really bad and you were diagnosed with it and God healed you.

00:20:54.009 --> 00:20:59.353
You have more compassion for that person, like I have for children with special needs.

00:20:59.354 --> 00:21:14.217
When I see a child with special needs in the store or whatever, my spirit literally weeps for them with the compassion that I have towards families that are going through this and I pray for them.

00:21:14.218 --> 00:21:21.465
I'm telling you, I have more compassion to pray for them than I have probably for anybody else because I've been through the pain.

00:21:21.466 --> 00:21:29.942
And when you walk through the pain of something, you're able to help somebody else that's going through it because you've been there. You've cried those tears.

00:21:29.943 --> 00:21:41.050
You've held your head up through the storm and you can say to them, 'Hey, you can make it, too.'And you may be going through the storm and thinking, 'Man, I don't know how I'm going to get through this.

00:21:41.051 --> 00:21:50.571
I don't know how I'm going to breathe another minute.'There were days I wanted to drive my car off the side of a bridge. I didn't care if I got hit by a train.

00:21:50.572 --> 00:21:57.279
That's how much pain I was going through on the way to work or on the way home because I knew what I was facing when I got there.

00:21:57.280 --> 00:22:01.635
But I fought through it because I knew that God had a plan for my life.

00:22:01.636 --> 00:22:11.435
But I'm talking about the darkest, darkest bottom of the pit, and you're thinking, 'I don't think I'm going to make this.'There were days that were that dark.

00:22:11.436 --> 00:22:19.759
I'm just being real with y'all. You may not want to hear that, but it's real. This is raw. It's real, and you need to hear it.

00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:35.759
There were days that I thought, while cleaning, and you didn't have enough money to buy a gallon of milk, and you're thinking, 'God, I don't know how I'm going to make it.'Those days when you're crying yourself to sleep and nobody around you cares.

00:22:35.760 --> 00:22:41.980
Nobody around you is praying for you. You felt like you're all alone. That's how I felt a lot of times.

00:22:41.981 --> 00:22:49.393
I'd go to work, being there in the bathrooms by myself cleaning, hearing my wife cry, calling on the phone, crying, 'I need your help.

00:22:49.394 --> 00:23:01.213
Pray for me. I'm having a hard day with Megan. I need this, I need that.'I was having a hard time myself, trying to pick myself up from this, and you think inside, 'But God.

00:23:01.214 --> 00:23:10.983
But God.'My hope is built on nothing less than Jesus's blood and His righteousness.

00:23:10.984 --> 00:23:18.079
I believe with all my heart that by the stripes of Jesus, Megan is healed.

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:25.699
And in the process of believing for the full manifestation—sometimes it's a process, but a miracle is a miracle.

00:23:25.700 --> 00:23:34.272
Even if it's day-to-day, if you're seeing change, it's still a miracle.

00:23:34.273 --> 00:23:44.485
Jesus... sometimes it's a progressive thing. I've seen it in my own life and I still believe, and I'm still standing.

00:23:44.486 --> 00:23:52.569
And people say, 'Well, shouldn't you have your full manifestation yet?'I've given up on trying to sit there and figure things out.

00:23:52.570 --> 00:24:03.047
I trust Him. In Him, I trust with all my heart, all my mind, all my soul, and all my strength.

00:24:03.048 --> 00:24:14.356
I lean not unto my own understanding, but in all thy ways acknowledge Him, and He said, 'He shall direct your paths.'I lean not unto my own understanding because I have a thousand and one things...

00:24:14.357 --> 00:24:18.354
why... you could get upset about it and say, 'Well, Lord, do you hear my prayers?

00:24:18.355 --> 00:24:23.262
Lord, where are you at? Why has the full manifestation of this not happened yet?

00:24:23.263 --> 00:24:31.766
Why is she still not talking? Why is she still doing this? Why is she still doing that?'But I say, 'I trust you, Father.

00:24:31.767 --> 00:24:43.359
Not my will, but yours be done.'When the manifestation comes—with the full manifestation, God—we give you all the glory, all honor, and all the praise regardless.

00:24:43.360 --> 00:24:52.479
I choose to worship you. I choose to worship you. And that's where we remain concerning these things.

00:24:52.480 --> 00:24:57.748
I used to always complain, 'Like I said, I can't go out and lay hands on these people.

00:24:57.749 --> 00:25:06.401
I can't do all this stuff.'And the Lord said, 'Brandon, Megan does not validate my word in the manifestation of her healing.

00:25:06.402 --> 00:25:10.908
My word validates itself. It's a pillar and it stands alone.

00:25:10.909 --> 00:25:20.909
I don't need Megan's full manifestation for you to go out and tell people that I'm a healer and lay hands on people and see them recover.

00:25:20.910 --> 00:25:32.530
My word is enough. My word is enough. I don't need you to have a full manifestation of something for you to do in obedience what I've called you to do.

00:25:32.531 --> 00:25:40.479
Do what I called you to do and don't worry about the rest.'My word is a pillar.

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:53.119
When He said, 'By my stripes you are healed,'in Galatians, Christ redeemed me from the curse of the law and He told me, He said, 'That's the foundation regardless.'I'm not moved by what I see.

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:57.912
I'm not moved by what I feel. I'm moved by what the word of God says.

00:25:57.913 --> 00:26:10.731
So back to what I was saying right before, when I'm taken out of my body and I'm standing at the hospital in this portal, I went through all this stuff and He's doing all this, I could feel the sun.

00:26:10.732 --> 00:26:27.994
I could feel the pressure. I could see the strain, all of it. And he said, this is what he said to me: 'Go back and give your daughter a hug and love on her and thank her right now for everything that's going on with your life.

00:26:27.995 --> 00:26:38.758
Thank her. Don't curse it anymore. Just stay in an atmosphere of praise, not towards her, but towards me.

00:26:38.759 --> 00:26:41.903
Change the complaining,'because I was complaining all the time.

00:26:41.904 --> 00:26:50.749
I was complaining about, 'I don't like being, I don't want to raise this, I don't want to do that.'I was always mean; my mouth was terrible, speaking things out of my mouth.

00:26:50.750 --> 00:26:57.034
'I don't want to do this anymore. I don't want to live this anymore.'And I got to the point where I said, 'Thank you, Father.

00:26:57.035 --> 00:27:01.829
Thank you. Thank you.'And then I got home and I held Megan. I said, 'Megan, I love you.

00:27:01.830 --> 00:27:07.273
I just want to tell you I love you and Daddy's sorry that I didn't hear Him right, but thank you.

00:27:07.274 --> 00:27:25.122
Your life is changing me. The Lord through you, Megan, is changing your daddy.'That was hard. The Lord through you is changing a man that needed help.

00:27:25.123 --> 00:27:35.274
And I'm sorry I had to be like this, but I thank you for your life and I pray for you and it's going to get better.

00:27:35.274 --> 00:27:41.766
But all things work together for good for those that love the Lord. And some people may not want to hear that.

00:27:41.767 --> 00:27:59.831
But sometimes people need to hear reality: whenever you're going through something and the storms of life are trying to knock you down, you've got to keep on keeping on and believe that all things are possible to him that believes and that Jesus is the healer still today—yesterday, today, and forever.

00:27:59.832 --> 00:28:03.751
And the same God that healed the sick back then is healing the sick today.

00:28:03.752 --> 00:28:08.432
And you cannot give up on what you're believing for. Do not give up on your unsaved loved ones.

00:28:08.433 --> 00:28:14.982
Do not give up on your unhealed ones that don't have the full manifestation of what they're believing for.

00:28:14.983 --> 00:28:21.372
